                            text: "Lu was born in China, has lived and worked in Australia and Turkey, and is currently based in Berlin, Germany. She has gained experience working for various agencies and product companies around the world. Formerly serving as the head of brand at Pitch, Lu has since embarked on her own freelance venture. She has had the privilege of working with esteemed teams such as Semplice, Fractal, BlueYard Capital, Veed, Breef, AEG, and more.",
