                            type: c,
                            text: "This talk explores the excitingly elusive realm of creative digital design where the unseen becomes the most essential element. We dive into the technical, yet poetic, concept of creative coding and reveal the artistry in the 3D spaces, the interplay of absence and presence, the silence and the noise. Embrace the undefined, the enigmatic, and the cryptic as we journey through the invisible dimensions of the digital world, reimagining the canvas of our creativity.",
